cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on improving semi-supervised learning in neural network architecture for language translation. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper introduces a hybrid supervised and unsupervised cost function to improve learning in neural networks. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a possibility as the paper mentions multi-scale kernels, which are commonly used in image processing. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as the paper discusses methods to improve performance of neural networks. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possibility as the paper focuses on improving learning in neural networks.
